Class MediaTypeRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.californium.core.coap.MediaTypeRegistry

  • public class MediaTypeRegistry
extends Object
    This class describes the CoAP Media Type Registry as defined in RFC 7252, Section 12.3.
